Module mesakit.plugins.josm.graph
Package com.telenav.mesakit.plugins.josm.graph.model

Class Selection

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.mesakit.plugins.josm.graph.model.Selection
public class Selection extends Object
Holds information about the currently selected objects and the stack of objects beneath the selection. Various isSelected() methods can be used to determine if an object is selected. The selection can be changed with the select() methods. The shapes of rendered objects can be stored with the shape() methods and hit testing is performed with the *ForPoint(Point2D) methods.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
